'''''Uranium''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|Lambda-class T-4a shuttle]] of the same group as [[Tydirium/Legends|''Tydirium'']]. It was found in [[Outpost 327]] when the latter was captured in the [[Mission to Zhar]].<ref name="Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance">''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]''</ref>

